1.5
log
@Some PCI machines do not implement the uperf registers.  Those that do
provide an 'sc at ebus'.  Use that instead of a direct attachment of
uperf to psycho.
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: uperf_psycho.c,v 1.4 2002/03/14 01:26:44 millert Exp $	*/

